{"tid":2220005,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美增輕型無人艦抗華","createTime":"2020-09-27T10:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T10:15:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ef84a8e1884995780c70d3a51596379cf5630316","tid":2220005,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T10:02:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200927/F5XZWRSHKBAYFJVXNKQTNXSISY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200927%2FF5XZWRSHKBAYFJVXNKQTNXSISY%2F&d=4SaXJ4tauImRU00LhBBHUqe24FYbdL6kC4fFNwqspTg%3D&h=e82316c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200927%2FF5XZWRSHKBAYFJVXNKQTNXSISY%2F&h=e9c04d19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200927/F5XZWRSHKBAYFJVXNKQTNXSISY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美增輕型無人艦抗華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5ru36OwRPLsPcXniCw4_-CHhvNQ=/2102x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NONDC2WIMRBVFGSESIQUYU4RFQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5ru36OwRPLsPcXniCw4_-CHhvNQ%3D%2F2102x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNONDC2WIMRBVFGSESIQUYU4RFQ.jpg&h=eb090360&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■較輕型艦艇將成美國在亞太海域抗衡中國的策略。 互聯網<br />\n<br />\n中國導彈系統規模近年急速擴張，美軍為應對威脅，計劃未來減少航空母艦數目，增加輕型和無人戰艦，圖以加強艦隊機動性取得優勢。<br />\n<br />\n美國原本計劃到2030年增加艦隻數目至355艘，並逐步將11艘尼米茲級航母更換成福特級。。。。。。。。。，令艦隊整體規模擴展至534艘，比中國十年後預料擁有的425艘多。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n艦艇將增至逾500艘<br />\n<br />\n文件上的數字都是來自今年4月《未來海軍力量研究》的草稿，研究者包括五角大樓的成本評估與計劃估算辦公室（CAPE）和哈德遜研究所的團隊，他們都認為有必要增加海軍艦船的數量和多樣性，以及提高垂直發射系統的能力。<br />\n<br />\n國防部欲大規模修改艦隊結構，。。。。。。。。。，評估無人艦與航母等載人艦之間的協調能力。<br />\n<br />\n海軍陸戰隊早前已提出要因應中國的情況調整過去的作戰模式，如配備較輕的裝備讓部隊可在太平洋島嶼之間進行突襲和撤離，並加入陸基導彈作為攻擊岸上目標的武器。<br />\n<br />\n美國《防務新聞》"},{"pid":"e488d13d4a08fb7060ee0a86359775db885a0674","tid":2220005,"uid":297997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T10:03:57.000Z","msg":"邊個怕美國"},{"pid":"1a7c1bb3924cae5c467b32cf592f4aa9bdb3c329","tid":2220005,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T10:04:58.000Z","msg":"China Joe上台，增乜都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"098fdc80831b8f01c7aaf449c9ebaa5b95074102","tid":2220005,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T10:15:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}